By submitting User-Generated Content on our Services, you grant us a non-exclusive, transferable, sub-licensable, royalty-free, worldwide license to use, store, display, reproduce, modify, create derivative works, perform, and distribute your User-Generated Content on our Services and through any other channels, including marketing and advertising materials.
